-- pd.component: Rubik - fpm font
name: https://github.com/heulitig/rubik

This component consist of Inter font with all it's styles from Thin-100 to Black-900.



-- pd.hidden-code: How to use

include heulitig.github.io/rubik package into FPM.ftd file

\-- fpm.dependency: heulitig.github.io/rubik

\-- fpm.auto-import: heulitig.github.io/rubik as rubik

Inside your .ftd file to change for any specific token use:

\-- fpm.type.headline-small.font: $rubik.fonts.Inter

\-- ftd.text:
role: $fpm.type.headline-small